room_title: Escape room "Hard Time" by Lubbock Escapes in Lubbock
room_description: Your team of elite army file clerks has been mistaken for an infamous crack commando unit. Accused and convicted of crimes you didn't commit, you are one hour away from being transferred to a maximum security stockade for the remainder of your soon-to-be miserable lives. Another file clerk, posing as a hardened jailer, believes you are innocent and has laid the foundation for your escape! Handcuffed and separated, your team must somehow work together to escape.
